    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a medium-low heat</p><p>Once hot, crack your <strong>egg[s]</strong> into the pan</p><p>Cover with a lid and cook for 2-3 min or until done to your liking</p><p>Tip: Give your egg a little shake before you crack for a perfectly centred yolk!</p>",
