    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the stir-fry sauce is fragrant, add the <strong>cooked rice </strong>with your <strong>blanched peas </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until the peas are warmed through – this is your <strong>Chinese-style veggie fried rice</strong></p>",
